<citation type="journal article" date="2002" name="Cell" volume="108" first="195" last="205">
<title>FtsK is a DNA motor protein that activates chromosome dimer resolution by switching the catalytic state of the XerC and XerD recombinases.</title>
<authorList>
<person name="Aussel L."/>
<person name="Barre F.-X."/>
<person name="Aroyo M."/>
<person name="Stasiak A."/>
<person name="Stasiak A.Z."/>
